desc: HERMOSA BEACH YOUTH MUSIC presents "STAR WARS: THE FORCE AWAKENS" Your ticket purchase will help raise funds for the band and chorus . ?Hermosa Beach Youth Music is a 501 (c)(3) non profit organization founded in 2012. ?Managed by a team of parent volunteers , HBYM is dedicated to providing the best music education for Hermosa Beach School kids.
